# Preamble
This license is an amendment to Urban Games' original Transport Fever 2 Modding Permissions and the Steam End User License Agreement, as well as the original mod author's license terms.

Any conflicting regulations made in this amendment are automatically voided and superceeded by the respective regulations made in the three original license agreements.

Urban Games Modding Guideline and Permissions for Creators
https://www.transportfever2.com/wiki/doku.php?id=modding:publishing

Steam EULA
